-4c3a-a0c1-2056e58e691c' class='xr-section-summary-in' type='checkbox'  checked><label for='section-4b023b3f-c421-4c3a-a0c1-2056e58e691c' class='xr-section-summary' >Attributes: <span>(4)</span></label><div class='xr-section-inline-details'></div><div class='xr-section-details'><dl class='xr-attrs'><dt><span>title :</span></dt><dd>temperature across weather stations</dd><dt><span>standard_name :</span></dt><dd>air_temperature</dd><dt><span>units :</span></dt><dd>degree_c</dd><dt><span>description :</span></dt><dd>simple example of an xarray.DataArray</dd></dl></div></li></ul></div></div>
